WEBVTT

00:07:59.548 --> 00:08:01.634
the girls cross the atrium.

00:08:01.634 --> 00:08:03.094
The slaves, young and old,

00:08:03.094 --> 00:08:04.174
male and female,

00:08:04.174 --> 00:08:06.639
await the return of their owner.

00:08:06.639 --> 00:08:09.368
When he returns, he may exact vengeance,

00:08:09.368 --> 00:08:11.784
ensuring his power over the slaves

00:08:11.784 --> 00:08:14.813
is maintained through violence and terror,

00:08:14.813 --> 00:08:17.967
to which any slave could be subjected.

00:08:17.967 --> 00:08:20.552
But, for the girls, they head upstairs for the night,

00:08:20.552 --> 00:08:22.382
ready for bed.